Revision history for Perl extension Template::Plugin::NoFollow

    - new "allow" option, which lets you specify regexes for URLs that -are-
      allowed to be followed; useful when processing large blocks of text that
      may contain internal links

1.000   Wed Sep 20 9:41pm 2006
    - updated test suites
    - now allows for filter to be named (e.g. "USE foo=NoFollow")
    - replaces existing rel="nofollow" attributes instead of creating
      duplicate attribute

0.01    Fri Mar 17 12:11pm 2006
    - original version
